---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Session Summary — SessionFS" activeNav="features" description="Automatic session summaries — files, tests, commands extracted in seconds.">
<section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-5 noise">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 mb-20">
        <div class="lg:w-1/2">
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6" style="font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans';">Know what happened.<br>In 10 seconds.</h1>
          <p class="text-lg mb-4" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Every session automatically summarized — files changed, tests run, commands executed, key decisions made. No more reading 2,000 messages to understand what the AI did.</p>
          <p class="text-lg mb-8" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Deterministic extraction runs instantly with no LLM cost. Parses pytest, jest, and go test output automatically.</p>
          <a href="/summary/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-semibold rounded-lg px-6 py-3 text-white hover:brightness-110 transition" style="background: #4f9cf7;">Read the docs</a>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full">
          <div class="term">
            <div class="term-bar"><div class="term-dot" style="background:#ff5f57"></div><div class="term-dot" style="background:#febc2e"></div><div class="term-dot" style="background:#28c840"></div><span class="ml-3 text-[13px]" style="color:#9ca3af; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;">session summary</span></div>
            <div class="p-5 text-sm space-y-3" style="font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;">
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold" style="color: #e6edf3;">Debug auth middleware</div>
                <div style="color: #9ca3af;">2.3h &middot; 327 msgs &middot; 28 tool calls</div>
                <div style="color: #9ca3af;">Claude Code &middot; feature/auth-fix @ a1b2c3d</div>
              </div>
              <div style="border-top: 1px solid #30363d;" class="pt-3">
                <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1" style="color: #9ca3af;">Files</div>
                <div class="text-[13px]" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Modified: <span style="color: #e6edf3;">middleware.py, tokens.py, test_auth.py</span></div>
                <div class="text-[13px]" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Read: <span style="color: #9ca3af;">config.py, user.py + 3 more</span></div>
              </div>
              <div style="border-top: 1px solid #30363d;" class="pt-3">
                <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1" style="color: #9ca3af;">Activity</div>
                <div class="text-[13px]" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Tests: <span style="color: #3ddc84;">5 passed</span>, <span style="color: #f04060;">1 failed</span></div>
                <div class="text-[13px]" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Commands: 34 &middot; Packages: pyjwt, redis</div>
              </div>
              <div style="border-top: 1px solid #30363d;" class="pt-3">
                <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider mb-1" style="color: #9ca3af;">Outcome</div>
                <div class="text-[13px]" style="color: #3ddc84;">Fix applied. 5/6 tests passing.</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="glass p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">No LLM needed</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Deterministic extraction parses tool calls directly. Files, commands, test results, packages, and errors — extracted in milliseconds.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Test framework support</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Parses pytest ("5 passed, 1 failed"), jest ("Tests: 10 passed"), and go test ("ok/FAIL") output automatically.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="glass p-6">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Dashboard + CLI</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #c9d1d9;">Summary tab in the dashboard with metric cards. CLI with <code style="color: #3ddc84;">sfs summary --today</code> for daily overviews.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
